1. New Balance Men's MW928 Walking Shoe - Available in 2E, 4E, and 6E widths, the MW928 is a supportive shoe for wide feet with a largest size of 18.
2. Brooks Men's Ghost 13 Running Shoe - A comfortable running shoe with a soft and breathable upper, available in 2E and 4E widths and largest size of 16.
3. Clarks Women's Un Adorn Zip Slip-On Sneaker - This slip-on sneaker is available in D and E widths, with a largest size of 12 and features a cushioned footbed and breathable upper for all-day comfort.
